&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree required and CFA charter holder preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;8+ years of dedicated experience in investment risk management, portfolio analytics, or a closely related investment oversight function, ideally within a buy-side asset management environment.&lt;/li&gt;
