&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in the preparation and execution of monthly accounting close activities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare and post journal entries in accordance with firm accounting policies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reconcile the firm’s cash accounts on a monthly basis.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the preparation of financial reports and management reporting packages.&lt;/li&gt;
