&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Accounts Receivable &amp;amp; Client Billing&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Calculate and process management fees in accordance with client agreements and upload fee statements to the portals of select clients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review billing calculations for accuracy and compliance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help maintain billing calendars and ensure timely completion of billing cycles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Apply client payments to accounts receivables ledger and research discrepancies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Produce accounts receivable aging reports and collection metrics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
