&lt;li&gt;1-3 years of experience in corporate finance, accounting, financial analysis, or related experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in investment management, asset management, financial services, banking, or public accounting is a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent attention to detail and data accuracy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with AI, Power BI, Tableau, or similar business intelligence tools is a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong written and verbal communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;
