&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Summary:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Senior Product Specialist will be responsible for supporting the positioning, enhancement and development of GW&amp;amp;K’s investment offerings for all channels, specifically Institutional, Advisory and Private Wealth. This will include understanding and identifying market trends as well as client needs.&lt;/p&gt;
